OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782728295
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter three-year-old girl found dead
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after the death of a three-
OL,8,Fyear-old girl in Surrey.
OL,10,FSurrey Police said the girl was found
OL,11,Fdead after they were called to a
OL,12,Fproperty in Chertsey on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe 31-year-old man was arrested at
OL,15,Fthe property in Pyrcroft Road and was
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,18,FPolice, who were called to the address
OL,19,Faround 5.40pm following concern of
OL,20,Fsafety reports, said he would be taken
OL,21,Finto custody once he had been treated.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
