PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782728295
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter three-year-old girl found dead
OL,6,FSurrey Police's major crime team is
OL,7,Fleading an investigation into the
OL,8,Fdeath with a statement from the force
OL,9,Fsaying they believed it happened
OL,10,F"within a family setting" and they
OL,11,Fwere not looking for anyone else in
OL,12,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,14,FA spokesperson from the major crime
OL,15,Fteam said: "This is a tragic incident,
OL,16,Fand our officers are working hard to
OL,17,Fbuild a picture of what happened.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@YO]wD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
