OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782728295
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter three-year-old girl found dead
OL,6,F"We have made an arrest in connection
OL,7,Fwith this incident and at this stage,
OL,8,Fwe are not looking to identify anyone
OL,9,Felse in connection with our
OL,10,Finvestigation. We have no reason to
OL,11,Fbelieve there is any risk to the
OL,12,Fpublic."
OL,14,F"There is a significant police
OL,15,Fpresence in Pyrcroft Road and this
OL,16,Fwill remain over the coming days.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782728295
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter three-year-old girl found dead
OL,6,F"We appreciate that the incident
OL,7,Fitself, as well as the significant
OL,8,Fpolice presence, will be concerning
OL,9,Ffor local residents and we would like
OL,10,Fto thank them for their co-operation
OL,11,Fas we conduct our investigation."
OL,13,FEight bouquets of flowers have been
OL,14,Fleft at the entrance to Syward Place,
OL,15,Fa flat complex on the corner of
OL,16,FPycroft Road and Bell Bridge Road.
OL,18,FThere is no longer a police presence
OL,19,Foutside the building, but officers can
OL,20,Fbe seen in the reception area and
OL,21,Falong a corridor on the ground floor.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
