OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782728295
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter three-year-old girl found dead
OL,6,FResidents living close to the scene
OL,7,Fwere mostly unaware that an alleged
OL,8,Fmurder had taken place inside Syward
OL,9,FPlace.
OL,11,FOne said: "I'm surprised, that's very
OL,12,Funusual for Chertsey".
OL,14,FAnother said: "It's tragic. Things
OL,15,Flike that don't happen around here."
OL,26,@sD@KOUtD@UO]vD@OOUwD@dO]
